::Prowl::

Prowl lets out a breath of relief. At least Iron Raptor had calmed down.

He feels slightly annoyed when Iron Raptor looked at his wounds. He had been 
blown to bits more times than he could count, these wounds weren't too bad. 
It was only fair, though, Prowl worried about her, and she was worrying about 
him.

He transforms into beast mode and lands on a nearby branch. His beast mode 
wasn't much of a walker.

"Owls don't walk too well..." Prowl says, shaking his head, "I think flying 
would be easier."
